=Introduction=

Model completion is the ability for the development environment to automatically complete much of the scaffolding of the model.

For more information, read [http://openiaml.org/#completion our paper submitted to ASWEC 2010], in particular our slides on how the process is [http://openiaml.org/publications/aswec-2010-slides.pdf currently implemented].
